desc: Grow your own houseplants from seeds. Strelitzia, Monstera, Philodendron and more interesting houseplant seeds are available in small quantities. Pot, nurture and enliven your indoor spaces.

layout.text:
Like you, we love to live amongst houseplants.
Whether you like showy, glossy leaves or dainty, trailing vines, Seed Seed™ sources fresh seeds so you can feel the buzz of sprouting your own seeds. All seeds are located in New Zealand.
MONSTERA • PHILODENDRON • STRELITZIA • SCHEFFLERA • FICUS • TILLANDSIA • MIMOSA • HYPOESTES • SANSEVIERIA & More
